== pawfaliki-0.5.2 (15/09/2007 )==
* Fixed another big hole where files in directories other than Pages could be edited. (Gregor Gresak)

== pawfaliki-0.5.1 (03/06/2007) ==
* Fixed security hole where pages could be created on the server with .extensions! (DanBethell)
* Should be a lot more XHTML valid. (Jari Seppälä)

== pawfaliki-0.5.0 (26/01/2006) ==
* Added support for locking entire wiki using HTTPAUTH. (DanBethell & AndyPreston)
* Fixed bug in updateWiki(). (AndyPreston)
* Fixed bug in RSS feed. (MarcVinyes)
* Fixed bug in image alignment code. (AndyPreston)
* Fixed bug where $ symbols broke stuff. (DanBethell)

== pawfaliki-0.4.5 (15/06/2005) ==
* Support for an external config file. (DanBethell)
* Fixed a few typos. (DanBethell)
* Support for anchor links in current page [[#example]]. (DanBethell)
* Ability to hide wiki controls. (DanBethell)
* Ability to enable 'debug mode'. (DanBethell)
* Cosmetic fixes for IE etc. (MarcVinyes)
* Updated the example CSS file. (MarcVinyes)
* Support for 'password required' text in the edit button. (MarcVinyes)
* Due to various issues pages are now only HTML4.01 Transitional compliant. (DanBethell)
* Some documentation. (DanBethell)

== pawfaliki-0.4.0 (09/05/2005) ==
* Backup & restore with zlib compression (if enabled). (DanBethell)
* Email page changes. (DanBethell)
* RSS feed of recently modified pages. (DanBethell)
* Restricted access support with password protection. (MarcVinyes)
* Support for multiple licenses. (DanBethell)
* Syntax info block on edit page. (DanBethell)
* Support for using functions in other php scripts. (DanBethell)
* Specify wiki pages using [[]] tags. (MarcVinyes)
* Ability to disable auto-generated WikiLinks. (MarcVinyes)
* Ability to enable HTML in wiki pages. (MarcVinyes)
* Better error handling. (MarcVinyes)
* Support for targets in links. (MarcVinyes)
* Support for images in link syntax. (DanBethell)
* Syntax for page anchors. (DanBethell)
* Misc. extra configuration options. (DanBethell)
* Very limited localised text support. (DanBethell)
* Fixed some misc. bugs. (DanBethell)
* Tidied up the code. (DanBethell)
* Brand new README & INSTALL files. (DanBethell)

== pawfaliki-0.3.0 (11/11/2004) ==
* Rewritten parser maintains whitespace without having to use the <PRE> tag. (DanBethell)
* All pages are now html4.01 strict compliant. (DanBethell)
* Ip blocking now enabled. Even works with wildcards. (DanBethell)

== pawfaliki-0.2.0 (10/11/2004) ==
* Added CSS support. (DanBethell)
* Fixed wordwrapping bugs. (DanBethell)
* Fixed coloured text bugs. (DanBethell)
* Everything should be transitional html4.0 compliant. (DanBethell)
* Added licensing information. (DanBethell)
* Added locking page support. (DanBethell)

== pawfaliki-0.1.0 (10/08/2004) ==
* Initial version of everything. (DanBethell)
